            <entry xml:id="entry_fæsmærun" xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                <form type="lemma"><orth>fæsmærun</orth><form type="participle"
                        ><orth>fæsmard</orth></form></form>
                <usg><lang/></usg>
                <sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>знать</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>know</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>быть знакомым</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>be acquainted with</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>узнавать</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>learn</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>вспоминать</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>remember</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                <re>
                    <form type="lemma"><orth>fæsmard</orth></form>
                    <sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>знакомый</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>familiar</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense>
                </re>
                <re>
                    <form type="lemma"><orth>ævæsmard</orth></form>
                    <sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>незнакомый</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>unfamiliar</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense>
                </re>
                <abv:exampleGrp>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>Alibeg je ʽrvaddælti ... ew ustur komi isserdta bæxgæs æma galgæsæj;
                            kæræʒej ærfæsmardtoncæ</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>Алибег нашел своих братьев в одном большом ущелье в качестве
                                табунщика и пастуха; они узнали друг друга</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>Alibeg found his brothers in a great gorge as a herd and a shepherd;
                                they recongnized each other</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_СОПам."/><biblScope>II
                            98</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>xæʒar ændær xuzæn ne ʽscæj, ma ʽj næbal bafæsmardta</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>дом-то стал другого вида, и он его больше не узнал</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>the house now looked different, and he no longer recognized it</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_MSt."
                            /><biblScope>5%l12–13%l</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>osæ dær æj mæsugi særæj bafæsmardta</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>жена тоже узнала его с верхушки башни</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>his wife also recognized him from the top of the tower</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_MSt."
                            /><biblScope>14%l2–3%l</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>suvællon næbal dæn, fæsmærun bajdædton card</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>я уже не ребенок, я стала понимать жизнь</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>I am no longer a child, I began to understand life</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Gurdž._Æduli"
                                /><biblScope>101</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>Agundæj ba de ʽvæsmard ængaræ osæn ku fæxxæssuj</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>Агунду твой незнакомый сверстник увозит в жены</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>your unfamiliar peer takes Agunda as his wife</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_СОПам."/><biblScope>II
                            50</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>dæ kʼox min ærxæssæ me ʽvæsmard ældar</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>дай мне свою руку, незнакомый мой алдар</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>give me your hand, my unfamiliar aldar</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_СОПам."/><biblScope>II
                            129</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Из %ifæ-smær-%i ← %i*pati-šmar-%i, сращение преверба %ipati-%i
                    (→%ifæ%i) с основой (%iš%i)%imar-%i, <mentioned xml:lang="ine"><lang/>
                        <w>*(s)mer-</w>
                        <gloss><q>думать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ine"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>помнить</q></gloss></mentioned> и пр. Ср. <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>šumurdan</w>
                        <gloss><q>считать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"
                            ><w>šumār</w>
                        <gloss><q>число</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>счет</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>расчет</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ku"><lang/>
                        <w>ažmārdin, žimārtin</w>
                        <gloss><q>считать</q></gloss></mentioned> (из перс.), <mentioned
                        xml:lang="ps"><lang/>
                        <w>šmērəl</w>
                        <gloss><q>считать</q></gloss></mentioned> (из перс.), <mentioned
                        xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
                        <w>*š%ru%rmār-</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">
                            (%išmʼr-%i)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en"> (%išmʼr-%i)</note>
                        <gloss><q>думать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sog"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>размышлять</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sog"
                            ><w>*pat-s%ru%rmar-</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">
                            (%iptšmʼr%i)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en">
                            (%iptšmʼr%i)</note>
                        <gloss><q>считать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kho"><lang/>
                        <w>mara-</w>
                        <gloss><q>сообщать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kho"
                            ><w>pammara-</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru"> (=
                            %i*pati-šmar%i)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en"> (=
                            %i*pati-šmar%i)</note>
                        <gloss><q>знать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>(š)mar-</w>
                        <gloss><q>замечать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>примечать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>помнить</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>paiti-šmar-</w>
                        <gloss><q>вспоминать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>думать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/>
                        <w>smar-</w>
                        <gloss><q>помнить</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>вспоминать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"
                            ><w>prati-smar-</w>
                        <gloss><q>вспоминать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="got"><lang/>
                        <w>maurnan</w>
                        <gloss><q>заботиться</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/>
                        <w>μέρμερος</w>
                        <gloss><q>озабоченный</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"><lang/>
                        <w>memor</w>
                        <gloss><q>помнящий</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"
                            ><w>memoria</w>
                        <gloss><q>память</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>воспоминание</q></gloss></mentioned> и пр. Ср. эту же основу с
                    другим превербом в %iny-mær%i [<ref type="xr" target="#entry_nymær"/>] |
                    %ini-mær%i ‘про себя’. Не из аланского ли идет венгерское <mentioned
                        xml:lang="hu"><lang/>
                        <w>ismer-</w>
                        <gloss><q>знать</q></gloss></mentioned>?%n<bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._Gr."/><biblScope>32, 57</biblScope></bibl>. —
                            <bibl><author>Залеман</author><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_ИАН"
                            /><biblScope xml:lang="ru">1907, стр. 549</biblScope><biblScope
                            xml:lang="en">1907, p. 549</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_ОЯФ_I"/><biblScope>119</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">From %ifæ-smær-%i ← %i*pati-šmar-%i, a contraction of the
                    preverb %ipati-%i (→%ifæ%i) with the stem (%iš%i)%imar-%i, <mentioned
                        xml:lang="ine"><lang/>
                        <w>*(s)mer-</w>
                        <gloss><q>think</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ine"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>remember</q></gloss></mentioned> etc. Cf. <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>šumurdan</w>
                        <gloss><q>count</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"
                            ><w>šumār</w>
                        <gloss><q>number</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>счет</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>calculation</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ku"><lang/>
                        <w>ažmārdin, žimārtin</w>
                        <gloss><q>count</q></gloss></mentioned> (from Persian), <mentioned
                        xml:lang="ps"><lang/>
                        <w>šmērəl</w>
                        <gloss><q>count</q></gloss></mentioned> (from Persian), <mentioned
                        xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
                        <w>*š%ru%rmār-</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">
                            (%išmʼr-%i)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en"> (%išmʼr-%i)</note>
                        <gloss><q>think</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sog"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>ponder</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sog"
                            ><w>*pat-s%ru%rmar-</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">
                            (%iptšmʼr%i)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en">
                            (%iptšmʼr%i)</note>
                        <gloss><q>count</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kho"><lang/>
                        <w>mara-</w>
                        <gloss><q>tell</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kho"
                            ><w>pammara-</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru"> (=
                            %i*pati-šmar%i)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en"> (=
                            %i*pati-šmar%i)</note>
                        <gloss><q>know</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>(š)mar-</w>
                        <gloss><q>notice</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>note</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>remember</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>paiti-šmar-</w>
                        <gloss><q>recall</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>think</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/>
                        <w>smar-</w>
                        <gloss><q>remember</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>recall</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"
                            ><w>prati-smar-</w>
                        <gloss><q>recollect</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="got"><lang/>
                        <w>maurnan</w>
                        <gloss><q>take care of</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/>
                        <w>μέρμερος</w>
                        <gloss><q>concerned</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"><lang/>
                        <w>memor</w>
                        <gloss><q>remembering</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"
                            ><w>memoria</w>
                        <gloss><q>memory</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>recollection</q></gloss></mentioned> etc. Cf. the same root with
                    another preverb in %iny-mær%i [<ref type="xr" target="#entry_nymær"/>] |
                    %ini-mær%i ‘to oneself’. Is not <mentioned xml:lang="hu"><lang/>
                        <w>ismer-</w>
                        <gloss><q>know</q></gloss></mentioned> from Alan?%n<bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._Gr."/><biblScope>32, 57</biblScope></bibl>. —
                            <bibl><author>Zaleman</author><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_ИАН"
                            /><biblScope xml:lang="ru">1907, стр. 549</biblScope><biblScope
                            xml:lang="en">1907, p. 549</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_ОЯФ_I"/><biblScope>119</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
            </entry>
        </body>
